Read a rewrite.def file

Source: R/strj-rewrite.R
read_rewrite_def.Rd

Read a rewrite.def file

Usage

read_rewrite_def(
  def_path = system.file("def/rewrite.def", package = "audubon")
)

Arguments

def_path

Character scalar; path to the rewriting definition file.

Value

A list.

Examples

str(read_rewrite_def())
